## ğŸŒ **Data Sources**

| ğŸ“ Dataset               | ğŸ“ Description                                     | ğŸ”— Source |
|-------------------------|---------------------------------------------------|-----------|
| FAOSTAT Crop Yield      | Annual crop yield data for India (2013â€“2022)     | [FAO](https://www.fao.org/faostat/en/) |
